{"parentUuid":"dc7a624d-a61b-40f6-a0d9-2292d3c95d5e","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/alex/go/src/github.com/alexrybrown/streamline","sessionId":"6dec9a89-152c-46c3-bd75-eeb0d902cfd5","version":"2.1.71","gitBranch":"main","agentId":"a81f5ee73ec6b1b14","slug":"linear-crafting-newell","type":"progress","data":{"type":"query_update","query":"Disney Streaming open source GitHub Scala Go projects smithy4s 2024 2025"},"toolUseID":"search-progress-1","parentToolUseID":"toolu_01FAAwB4SXWffSyEjoeY1gZ7","uuid":"ac5c0c39-ef78-49b5-9693-7e11f2a79f4b","timestamp":"2026-03-07T19:29:55.720Z"}
{"parentUuid":"ac5c0c39-ef78-49b5-9693-7e11f2a79f4b","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/alex/go/src/github.com/alexrybrown/streamline","sessionId":"6dec9a89-152c-46c3-bd75-eeb0d902cfd5","version":"2.1.71","gitBranch":"main","agentId":"a81f5ee73ec6b1b14","slug":"linear-crafting-newell","type":"progress","data":{"type":"search_results_received","resultCount":10,"query":"Disney Streaming open source GitHub Scala Go projects smithy4s 2024 2025"},"toolUseID":"srvtoolu_01CEhmSjawoWEaLm6pF9tP2P","parentToolUseID":"toolu_01FAAwB4SXWffSyEjoeY1gZ7","uuid":"d2994b16-14a0-4a00-b4a3-43851f7c8007","timestamp":"2026-03-07T19:29:57.607Z"}
{"parentUuid":"7b651dcb-1276-4ba9-acd5-37a565206f88","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/alex/go/src/github.com/alexrybrown/streamline","sessionId":"6dec9a89-152c-46c3-bd75-eeb0d902cfd5","version":"2.1.71","gitBranch":"main","agentId":"a81f5ee73ec6b1b14","slug":"linear-crafting-newell","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01FAAwB4SXWffSyEjoeY1gZ7","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Disney Streaming open source GitHub Scala Go projects smithy4s 2024 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Disney Streaming · GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/disneystreaming\"},{\"title\":\"smithy4s\",\"url\":\"https://disneystreaming.github.io/smithy4s/\"},{\"title\":\"Disney Streaming\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/orgs/disneystreaming/repositories\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - disneystreaming/smithy4s: https://disneystreaming.github.io/smithy4s/\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/disneystreaming/smithy4s\"},{\"title\":\"Disney Open Source\",\"url\":\"https://disney.github.io/\"},{\"title\":\"disneyplus · GitHub Topics\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/topics/disneyplus\"},{\"title\":\"disney · GitHub Topics · GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/topics/disney?l=go&o=desc&s=\"},{\"title\":\"Releases · disneystreaming/smithy4s\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/disneystreaming/smithy4s/releases\"},{\"title\":\"Scaladex - disneystreaming / smithy4s\",\"url\":\"https://index.scala-lang.org/disneystreaming/smithy4s\"},{\"title\":\"Installation | smithy4s\",\"url\":\"https://disneystreaming.github.io/smithy4s/docs/overview/installation/\"}]\n\nHere's a summary of the search results related to **Disney Streaming's open source GitHub projects**, including their Scala, Go, and smithy4s work in 2024–2025:\n\n---\n\n## Disney Streaming on GitHub\n\nDisney Streaming's GitHub organization hosts repositories spanning multiple languages including Scala, Go, Java, TypeScript, and Shell. Their open source presence is available at [github.com/disneystreaming](https://github.com/disneystreaming).\n\n### Smithy4s — Flagship Scala Project\n\nSmithy4s uses the Smithy model you define to generate Scala code, including an interface that represents the service. This interface contains one method per service operation.\n\nPassing your service implementation to the SimpleRestJsonBuilder gives you an HttpRoutes instance that handles HTTP routing and JSON serialization/deserialization.\n\nThe project remains actively maintained:\n- The smithy4s repository was updated as recently as January 23, 2026, and has 393 stars and 105 forks.\n\n#### Recent Releases & Changes (2024–2025)\n\nRecent updates include adding HTTP method and pattern to Scaladoc, moving publishing to Sonatype Central, and switching back to the `com.disneystreaming` org for Alloy/smithy-translate.\n\nOne release included a version of Alloy published under `io.github.disneystreaming`, but since new and old versions of Alloy didn't get deconflicted by dependency resolution (causing conflicts/errors in Smithy's model loading), the change was reverted and rolled out in smithy4s 0.18.39.\n\n#### Installation\n\nsmithy4s-sbt-codegen is a code generating sbt plugin that creates `.scala` files corresponding to the provided `.smithy` specs. There is also a smithy4s-mill-codegen-plugin for mill users.\n\n### Related Repositories\n\nDisney Streaming also maintains repositories for Smithy IDL tooling (smithy-translate), Alloy (a Smithy-related library), and a build pipeline to publish AWS SDK specs to Maven Central.\n\n### Disney's Broader Open Source Program\n\nOpen Source Software is important to The Walt Disney Company, and Disney has established an Open Source Program to encourage developers to utilize, contribute to, and release software as Open Source.\n\nNotable projects highlighted on Disney's open source portal include:\n- **Weaver-Test** — a Scala test framework that integrates tightly with Cats-Effect, which is the root of a large subset of the Scala ecosystem.\n- **SSM helpers** — tools to manage systems with AWS Systems Manager, including `ssm-session` for interactive shells and `ssm-run` for running commands on multiple instances.\n\n---\n\nIn summary, Disney Streaming's most prominent open source project is **smithy4s**, a Scala code-generation tool based on the Smithy IDL that remains actively developed through 2024, 2025, and into 2026. They also maintain adjacent tooling (Alloy, smithy-translate) and various infrastructure/DevOps tools on GitHub.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"056af6f5-9072-4ea4-b206-daaac4c666c7","timestamp":"2026-03-07T19:30:19.101Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"7b651dcb-1276-4ba9-acd5-37a565206f88"}
