{"parentUuid":"d78109b5-a0f8-4cab-9306-7be7eefc8581","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/alex/go/src/github.com/alexrybrown/streamline","sessionId":"6dec9a89-152c-46c3-bd75-eeb0d902cfd5","version":"2.1.71","gitBranch":"main","agentId":"a63db3607a31f78d8","slug":"linear-crafting-newell","type":"progress","data":{"type":"search_results_received","resultCount":1,"query":"\"Warner Bros Discovery\" streaming conference NAB IBC 2024 2025"},"toolUseID":"srvtoolu_01Mv64k9ivXg8Pn6BHzju6SN","parentToolUseID":"toolu_01DCKx1geMcfNr1tAPXemwzw","uuid":"d2194a0a-a706-4d66-b63c-a20cd346259f","timestamp":"2026-03-07T19:40:52.875Z"}
{"parentUuid":"d2194a0a-a706-4d66-b63c-a20cd346259f","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/alex/go/src/github.com/alexrybrown/streamline","sessionId":"6dec9a89-152c-46c3-bd75-eeb0d902cfd5","version":"2.1.71","gitBranch":"main","agentId":"a63db3607a31f78d8","slug":"linear-crafting-newell","type":"progress","data":{"type":"search_results_received","resultCount":10,"query":"WBD streaming conference talk NAB IBC 2025"},"toolUseID":"srvtoolu_01J4uYdEXwqzA7UVaEhH4Cqk","parentToolUseID":"toolu_01DCKx1geMcfNr1tAPXemwzw","uuid":"88ec053c-220a-4d50-a43f-e85a3a37747b","timestamp":"2026-03-07T19:40:52.881Z"}
{"parentUuid":"3beb1135-01c6-4f74-9e01-7c84b75eafc0","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/alex/go/src/github.com/alexrybrown/streamline","sessionId":"6dec9a89-152c-46c3-bd75-eeb0d902cfd5","version":"2.1.71","gitBranch":"main","agentId":"a63db3607a31f78d8","slug":"linear-crafting-newell","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DCKx1geMcfNr1tAPXemwzw","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"\"Warner Bros Discovery\" OR \"WBD\" streaming conference talk NAB IBC 2024 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"April 2026 on Warner Bros Discovery - TV Central\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvcentral.com.au/streaming/discovery/april-2026-on-warner-bros-discovery/\"}]\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"IBC reveals 2025 conference programme\",\"url\":\"https://www.broadbandtvnews.com/2025/08/07/ibc-reveals-2025-conference-programme/\"},{\"title\":\"NAB 2025: Must-see Sessions - Momento\",\"url\":\"https://www.gomomento.com/blog/nab-2025-must-see-sessions/\"},{\"title\":\"Full IBC2025 conference line-up revealed - CSI Magazine\",\"url\":\"https://www.csimagazine.com/csi/ibc2025-full-conference.php\"},{\"title\":\"2025 NAB Streaming Summit Videos - NAB Show Streaming Summit\",\"url\":\"https://nabstreamingsummit.com/videos/videos-2025-lasvegas/\"},{\"title\":\"IBC2026 | IBC Convention Amsterdam: 11-14 Sep 26\",\"url\":\"https://show.ibc.org/\"},{\"title\":\"IBC 2025 Conference Program Showcases Media’s Defining Shifts Across Platforms, People and Technology\",\"url\":\"https://www.sportsvideo.org/2025/08/07/ibc-2025-conference-program-showcases-medias-defining-shifts-across-platforms-people-and-technology/\"},{\"title\":\"IBC2025 announces speakers from NBCUniversal, ITV, YouTube, WBD | Advanced Television\",\"url\":\"https://www.advanced-television.com/2025/05/12/ibc2025-announces-speakers-from-nbcuniversal-itv-youtube-wbd/\"},{\"title\":\"Wowza at NAB 2025 | Wowza\",\"url\":\"https://www.wowza.com/nab-book-a-meeting-2025\"},{\"title\":\"Latest News & Insight for Media & Entertainment | IBC365\",\"url\":\"https://www.ibc.org/home\"},{\"title\":\"IBC opens registration for 2025 edition - BroadcastPro ME\",\"url\":\"https://www.broadcastprome.com/ibc/ibc-opens-registration-for-2025-edition/\"}]\n\nHere's a summary of what I found regarding Warner Bros. Discovery (WBD) participation in streaming conferences at NAB and IBC in 2024–2025:\n\n---\n\n## NAB 2025 (Las Vegas, April 2025)\n\nNAB 2025 must-see sessions included Streaming Summit sessions from Warner Brothers Discovery (WBD) and FOX, along with AI presentations.\n\n### Key WBD Sessions at NAB 2025 Streaming Summit:\n\n1. **Scalable Cloud Video Stacks Panel:**\n   Jenny Hua from Warner Brothers Discovery, along with a panel from NBCUniversal, Wowza, and Sinclair, discussed strategies for architecting scalable cloud video stacks for FAST, Live, and SVOD workflows. This session took place on Monday, April 7, 1:30–2:30 PM.\n\n2. **Live Sports Streaming Workflows:**\n   The panel was moderated by Victoria Tuzova (Elecard) and included Steven Woodard (Warner Brothers Discovery), Derik Yarnell (Comcast), Steven Jalicy (ESL FACEIT GROUP), and Valeria Sosa (Netflix). This session was held on Tuesday, April 8, 2:45–3:45 PM, covering \"Live Sports Streaming Workflows: Real-Time Use Cases and Latest Technology Deployments.\"\n\n3. **Kids' Streaming Market (Connie Huang, WBD):**\n   Connie Huang, Software Engineering Manager at WBD, presented firsthand insights into the unique challenges of the kids' streaming market, explaining why a full architecture overhaul was necessary to future-proof the platform and providing practical insight into technical resource allocation and UX/video workflow innovation.\n\n4. **Scalable Streaming Architectures (Wowza-hosted panel):**\n   Wowza CEO Krish Kumar and engineering leaders from NBCU, Sinclair Broadcast Group, and WBD participated in a deep dive into strategies for building scalable, future-proof streaming architectures that support FAST, live, and SVOD delivery models.\n\n---\n\n## IBC 2025 (RAI Amsterdam, September 12–15, 2025)\n\nIndustry leaders from ABC, Fremantle, ITV, NBCUniversal, Sling TV, YouTube, and Warner Bros. Discovery were confirmed as speakers at the IBC Conference.\n\n### Key WBD Appearances at IBC 2025:\n\n1. **CTO Roundtable (Opening Day):**\n   The three-day conference kicks off on Friday, September 12, with a heavyweight CTO roundtable featuring Warner Bros. Discovery's Avi Saxena, ITV's Simon Farnsworth, and Paramount's Phil Wiser.\n\n2. **MovieLabs 2030 Vision Panel:**\n   MovieLabs President Richard Berger leads a panel with top technology executives from Walt Disney Studios, Sony Pictures, Warner Bros. Discovery, and Paramount, discussing their 2030 vision for collaborative content creation. Specifically, James Crossland, Executive Vice President and Head of Global Content Operations at Warner Bros. Discovery, is featured alongside Phil Wiser of Paramount Global and Eddie Drake of Walt Disney Studios.\n\n3. **Confirmed Speaker — Avi Saxena:**\n   Notable confirmed speakers include Avi Saxena of Warner Bros. Discovery, along with leaders from ABC, Fremantle, ITV, NBCUniversal, Sling TV, and YouTube EMEA.\n\n### IBC 2025 Conference Themes:\nCentral themes include AI-driven transformation, new rules of audience engagement, evolving streaming strategies, and future-proof production workflows, with sessions featuring both traditional broadcasters and next-gen platforms.\n\n---\n\nThe search results did not surface specific details about WBD sessions at **IBC 2024** or **NAB 2024** specifically, though the 2025 events clearly show WBD as a prominent participant across multiple streaming-focused panels and keynotes at both conferences.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"055023c2-4df0-4169-9ab9-3f162f834463","timestamp":"2026-03-07T19:41:16.446Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":