{"parentUuid":"e5812a44-e9cf-433d-ba2a-225a288ba00f","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/alex/go/src/github.com/alexrybrown/streamline","sessionId":"6dec9a89-152c-46c3-bd75-eeb0d902cfd5","version":"2.1.71","gitBranch":"main","agentId":"a63db3607a31f78d8","slug":"linear-crafting-newell","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011PjnUTcWjjjbJSeyYTLkkQ","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"site:wbdtechblog.com streaming video architecture infrastructure\"\n\nNo links found.\n\nIt appears the search returned no results for that specific query. This could mean:\n\n1. The site `wbdtechblog.com` may not have indexed content matching those exact terms.\n2. The domain may have changed or the blog may be hosted at a different URL.\n\nLet me try a broader search to find relevant content from Warner Bros. Discovery's tech blog.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Building the Future of Media & Entertainment Technology | by Warner Bros. Discovery | TECH @ WBD\",\"url\":\"https://wbdtechblog.com/building-the-future-of-media-entertainment-technology-b92c75c90563\"},{\"title\":\"Modern Data Streaming Architecture | by TransUnion Global Technology, Data & Analytics | Medium\",\"url\":\"https://medium.com/@techattu/modern-data-streaming-architecture-9d518c371066\"},{\"title\":\"Streaming Architecture. If you have been around the world of… | by Ronald Ssebalamu | Medium\",\"url\":\"https://medium.com/@ronaldssebalamu/streaming-architecture-cb23cf6e163b\"},{\"title\":\"Everything You Need to Know about Streaming Data Architecture\",\"url\":\"https://www.orientsoftware.com/blog/streaming-data-architecture/\"},{\"title\":\"The Right Data Architecture for Streaming Data\",\"url\":\"https://www.yugabyte.com/blog/streaming-data-architecture/\"},{\"title\":\"Streaming Data Architecture in 2023: Components & Examples | Upsolver\",\"url\":\"https://www.upsolver.com/blog/streaming-data-architecture-key-components\"},{\"title\":\"Why Stream? - Streaming Architecture [Book]\",\"url\":\"https://www.oreilly.com/library/view/streaming-architecture/9781491953914/ch01.html\"},{\"title\":\"What is a data streaming architecture?\",\"url\":\"https://www.redpanda.com/blog/data-streaming-architecture\"},{\"title\":\"Streaming Data Architecture in 2024: Components and Examples - RisingWave: Real-Time Event Streaming Platform\",\"url\":\"https://risingwave.com/blog/streaming-data-architecture-in-2024-components-and-examples/\"},{\"title\":\"Real-time streaming data architectures: how to build & scale\",\"url\":\"https://www.tinybird.co/blog/real-time-streaming-data-architectures-that-scale\"}]\n\nHere are the results from the search. The `site:wbdtechblog.com` query returned no results directly, but a broader search did find one result from the WBD Tech Blog along with several other related articles about streaming architecture.\n\n## Results from WBD Tech Blog (wbdtechblog.com)\n\nOnly one result was found from the WBD Tech Blog itself:\n\n**[Building the Future of Media & Entertainment Technology](https://wbdtechblog.com/building-the-future-of-media-entertainment-technology-b92c75c90563)** (April 22, 2025)\n\nThey are a team of gifted engineers, product managers, and operational experts building the technology behind Max, Eurosport, WB Games and more. With 116.9 million global Direct to Consumer subscribers, their technology connects fans to entertainment's most beloved brands. The journey to becoming the fastest growing streaming service hasn't been simple — in a span of only 9 months, Max launched in 75 new countries and 28 languages across Latin America, Europe, and Asia.\n\nAs they continue to drive innovation across core areas — Streaming, Gaming, Enterprise Technology, Product and Design — the blog offers access to their world of technology. Topics include engineering culture, AI/ML, operationalizing scale, UX & product design, interactive technology, and more.\n\nHowever, this is an introductory blog post and doesn't dive deeply into specific video streaming architecture or infrastructure details. The site may have additional articles on these topics that weren't indexed in the search results, or they may use different terminology. You might want to visit [wbdtechblog.com](https://wbdtechblog.com) directly and browse their articles for more specific content about streaming video architecture and infrastructure.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"cd16834e-d695-42e0-87f9-6ef77ef74cac","timestamp":"2026-03-07T19:46:56.006Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"e5812a44-e9cf-433d-ba2a-225a288ba00f"}
